ygData.messageBody:
*burp* well, repetedli doin Qeynos kwests will levitate your fakshion in
da Ashen Order....but I *hic* did that white headbnad kwest near 40 times.
Then I go to freeport an Puab still got no headband for me.

Next....pox on Kellios. He never showed me a helping hand. I got my bran
*hic* brandy an I got some iner peece an that be all I need at this *burp*
moment. Any monk that be followin Kellios's teechin's be in my opinyon,
not write in da head. *hic*

black perls, serpentin bracers and da execushoners hud.....and only 17.
Man that makes me mad....i canna stand monks or any class for dat mater
that *burp* that be waring stuff they canna earn on thay own *hic* Pox on
yu.

Sligo
Cazic Thule
